The paper deals with a machine learning approach (Information Bottleneck) and proposes a new method that combines it with neural networks (INNs) for classification tasks. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Information Theory (cs.IT).
